# research_state.md.template (RETIRED)

Replaced by workstream-local primary state objects:

- Capability / Technology Research: use `assets/rd/capability_map.md.template`
  (Layer 1 + Layer 2)
- Phenomenon / Mechanism Research: use
  `assets/pure_research/explanation_ledger.md.template`

`scripts/new_project.py` now creates a mixed project shell by default.
Workstreams select the local state object and gate. Passing
`--mode rd|pure-research` is only an initial-workstream shortcut inside that
mixed shell.

Do not use this template for new projects.
